1 tomato
1 packet croissants
1 packet Totara Tasty Cheddar

Preheat oven to 220°C/200°C fan-forced. Thinly slice Totara Tasty Cheddar. Thinly slice tomato. Cut croissants in half horizontally.

Divide Cheddar and tomato between croissant bases. Top with croissant tops and place on a baking tray. Bake until cheese is melted,
5-8 minutes.

Divide croissants between plates.